パッケージ xyz.mlserver.advancementcreator.shared

インタフェース SharedEnum

既知の実装クラスのリスト:
Dimension, Effect, Enchant, Feature, MaterialId, MobType, Potion, Trigger.Type
public interface SharedEnum
Enums implementing this interface are used to define data usually in SharedObjects. They can also be converted to a String to be used in JSON objects.
